🔟 Success

8️⃣ PRO STRATEGY (SELECTION SECRET)

👉 3 types of responses you should give:

1️⃣ Action-based
👉 “He solves problems efficiently”

2️⃣ Quality-based
👉 “Discipline builds strong character”

3️⃣ Real-life thinking
👉 “Time management increases productivity”

🧠 PSYCHOLOGY TRICK

👉 Don’t try to create fake personality
👉 Keep responses natural + consistent

💥 Same personality must appear in:

TAT

WAT

SRT

